body: "GH-601. dist/sdk/runtime.d.ts: PmActionOptions = Record<string, unknown> for mutation inputs; projected list rows equally untyped — field typos/wrong value types compile clean under strict and fail at runtime; listed-item id access not type-safe. Fix direction: derive per-action input types from the existing flag/schema contracts (single source, no hand-written duplicates) + typed projection rows; add type-level tests. Serves SDK-first (pm-usfg) consumer contract quality."
